The Coronavirus Dashboard

This Coronavirus dashboard provides an overview of the 2019 Novel Coronavirus COVID-19 (2019-nCoV) epidemic. This dashboard is built with R using the Rmakrdown framework and can easily reproduce by others.

The data behind this dashboard can be found in the following repository, and its update on a daily bases
